EvgS/EvgA induces the EvgA-YdeO-GadE cascade of AR gene regulation , and a branched pathway operating via SafA activates the PhoQ/PhoP system , leading to an enhanced level of cellular RpoS .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21193607" target="_blank">21193607</a>]<br></label>
